INSERT INTO
    fishing_weight_predictions (
    weight,catch_location_id,species_group_id,week,year
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::DOUBLE PRECISION[],$2::TEXT[],$3::INT[],$4::INT[],$5::INT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (catch_location_id, species_group_id, week, year) DO UPDATE SET weight = EXCLUDED.weight
